'''2016年夏季奥林匹克运动会女子4×100米自由泳接力比赛'''于2016年8月6日在[[巴西|巴西]][[里约热内卢|里约热内卢]]奥林匹克水上运动中心举行<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.rio2016.com/en/swimming-standings-sw-womens-4-x-100m-freestyle-relay|title=Women's 4×100m Freestyle Relay|publisher=Rio 2016|accessdate=2016-08-05|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160922160354/https://www.rio2016.com/en/swimming-standings-sw-womens-4-x-100m-freestyle-relay|archivedate=2016-09-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

由[[艾瑪·麥基翁|艾瑪·麥基翁]]、[[布里塔妮·埃尔姆斯利|布里塔妮·埃尔姆斯利]]、[[勃朗特·坎贝尔|勃朗特]]和[[凯特·坎贝尔|凯特·坎贝尔]]组成的澳大利亚队在本次比赛中表现出色，以3分30秒65的成绩打破了队伍保持的世界纪录，毫无悬念地夺得冠军<ref>{{cite news|first=Chris|last=Barrett|title=Rio Olympics 2016: Australia's women win gold in world record time in 4x100m freestyle relay|url=http://www.smh.com.au/sport/olympics/rio-2016/olympics-swimming/rio-olympics-2016-australias-women-win-gold-in-world-record-time-in-4x100m-freestyle-relay-20160807-gqmskw.html|publisher=[[雪梨晨鋒報|Sydney Morning Herald]]|date=2016-08-07|accessdate=2016-08-28|archive-date=2016-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160824124552/http://www.smh.com.au/sport/olympics/rio-2016/olympics-swimming/rio-olympics-2016-australias-women-win-gold-in-world-record-time-in-4x100m-freestyle-relay-20160807-gqmskw.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Cate, Bronte Campbell lead Australian women to 4x100m gold at Rio|url=http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/cate-bronte-campbell-lead-australian-women-4x100m-gold/story?id=41178620|publisher=ABC News Australia|date=2016-08-07|accessdate=2016-08-28|archive-date=2016-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828230247/http://abcnews.go.com/Sports/cate-bronte-campbell-lead-australian-women-4x100m-gold/story?id=41178620|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由[[西蒙娜·曼努埃尔|西蒙娜·曼努埃尔]]、[[阿比·魏策尔|阿比·魏策尔]]、[[达娜·沃尔默|达娜·沃尔默]]和[[姬蒂·雷德基|姬蒂·雷德基]]组成的美国队则以3分31秒89的成绩打破美洲纪录，获得一枚银牌<ref>{{cite news|first=Armen|last=Graham|title=Katie Ledecky helps relay team to silver as US swimmers begin strongly|url=https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/aug/06/katie-ledecky-silver-us-swimmers-rio-2016|publisher=[[卫报|The Guardian]]|date=2016-08-06|accessdate=2016-08-28|archive-date=2016-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160828023408/https://www.theguardian.com/sport/2016/aug/06/katie-ledecky-silver-us-swimmers-rio-2016|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而由[[桑德里娜·曼维尔|桑德里娜·曼维尔]]、[[尚塔尔·范兰德赫姆|尚塔尔·范兰德赫姆]]、[[泰勒·拉克|泰勒·拉克]]和[[佩妮·奥莱克夏克|佩妮·奥莱克夏克]]组成的加拿大队则以3分32秒89的成绩获得一枚铜牌，终结了加拿大女子游泳队20年来无奥运奖牌入账的纪录<ref>{{cite news|first=Benjamin|last=Blum|title=Canada wins bronze in women's 4x100m freestyle relay|url=http://olympics.cbc.ca/news/article/canadian-women-contention-for-swimming-medals.html|publisher=[[加拿大廣播公司|Canadian Broadcasting Corporation]]|date=2016-08-07|accessdate=2016-08-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825235736/http://olympics.cbc.ca/news/article/canadian-women-contention-for-swimming-medals.html|archivedate=2016-08-25}}</ref><ref name=W400RelayFR>{{cite news|title=Australians Clock World Record to Earn Olympic Gold in Women's 400 Freestyle Relay|url=https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/australians-clock-world-record-to-earn-olympic-gold-in-womens-400-freestyle-relay/|publisher=Swimming World Magazine|date=2016-08-06|accessdate=2016-08-28|archive-date=2019-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191108180743/https://www.swimmingworldmagazine.com/news/australians-clock-world-record-to-earn-olympic-gold-in-womens-400-freestyle-relay/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

本次比赛的奖牌有力争夺者荷兰队在这次比赛中以近1秒之差与奖牌失之交臂，而瑞典队、意大利队、法国队和日本队分获五至八名<ref name=W400RelayFR/>。

